Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:37.81,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:46.23,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて抱きしめてみるのは罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:53.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:58.78,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘆いても夢は唄わない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:04.80,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此所で叫んだよ「答えは誰が持ってるの？」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:09.27,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}俯いたままじゃ気付かない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:15.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君の瞳の中　未来を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:20.76,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もしも奇跡が今を指すなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.48,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}にじむ涙ぬぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.02,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}前を向いて歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:30.85,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:36.56,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}こんな苦しさで何も見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:41.66,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私よ燃えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:49.69,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}燃えて彼方へ　情熱は罪じゃないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:56.92,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}火で闇を祓え CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:37.81,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃尽我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:46.23,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}想用熊熊燃烧的胸怀抱紧你 这不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:53.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驱散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:58.78,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自哀之人怎能唱出梦想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:04.80,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}站在原地嘶吼“到底谁能给我答案？”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:09.27,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}抬起头来才能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:15.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你的瞳孔中有着我寻觅已久的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:20.76,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如果奇迹指向这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.48,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拭去盈眶的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.02,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向前大步前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:30.85,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}解放我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:36.56,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在如此的炼狱中会迷失前进的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:41.66,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}烈焰啊 燃尽我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:49.69,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}化为一道烈焰逝向彼方 这浑身的炙热不是罪孽吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:56.92,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}用烈焰驱散黑暗 CHOIR JAIL  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:15.72,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとりきりのさびしさ　ひとときのほほえみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:23.66,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれるものは　みんないとしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:33.35,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すぐそばにいても　触れられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:42.25,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心は月のように　形をかえていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:50.81,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かなわない約束も　かわかない涙も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:23:01.74,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれたものは　だきしめておどる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:15.72,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的孤独 一时间的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:23.66,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我带来的瑰宝 一样样都令人爱不释手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:33.35,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕两人之间的距离触手可及 可无形之壁注定你我天人永隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:42.25,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心宛如明月 阴晴圆缺不断变幻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:50.81,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定依旧无法实现 眼泪仍然不愿干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:23:01.74,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把你给的瑰宝 紧拥怀中蓦然舞起..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？夕..夕夕子学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点胖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！不可以看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法移开视线！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊..这是在夕子学姐的记忆之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂..难不成..！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 等一下 夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪之十 丧失少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个景色 60年前的记忆..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夕子学姐脑海中的..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是夕子学姐所丢弃的 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留在影夕子脑海中的记忆..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是无能为力..看到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸..胸部的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 夕子学姐的感觉也直接传达给了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒 内向 害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成这个人就是夕子学姐的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是雾江同学的..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要去那孩子那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为昨天小浅也没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多帮她做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连姐姐也染上瘟疫的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是普通的感冒而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫也说没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不该冒着危险去接近她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果为了那孩子 姐姐万一发生了什么不测..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要说这种话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在村子正经历一段很艰难的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不大家互相帮一把的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我又不是孩子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子小姐她..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连夕子学姐双唇的感触都..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小..小指头撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛..你才是振作一点啦 夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近以前是矿山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是出产铜矿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再给你东西吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中林先生家里..大家都去世了啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是诅咒石上记载的那场瘟疫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里死了好多人 然后夕子学姐成了人柱的那场..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小浅 今天感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了早餐来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我马上就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 这个是罐装的鱼肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通的罐头鱼的味道..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 在这个时代里罐头很难得吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经吃饱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 吃一颗糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在一起的话 夕子姐姐也会染上瘟疫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫也说了小浅得的不是瘟疫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人..夕子姐姐这个大骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈奶奶还有姐姐..大家都..大家都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家真的都很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小浅会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上也会因瘟疫而死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！夕子姐姐也会得瘟疫的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夕子姐姐死掉的话 我就..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个送给小浅做礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的时候 就把这个当成是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 是一对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的话心里怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉跟雾江同学好像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有和别人说过话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 总觉得大人们很吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家心里都不安地不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家一定在想解决的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事到底会持续到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我虽然不知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不可以失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连希望都失去的话 那一切就结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是村长他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要去学园吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是去讨论今后的对策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也应该去听一听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 村子就全没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 我们也束手无策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中林一家子真的很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一个人都没剩下..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家具衣服全拿去烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榻榻米和衣柜全都要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样已经是第几家了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家死于瘟疫的话这已经是第十三家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有超过一半的人家 家里都有一两个人得病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也..活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 就坐等着所有人一起完蛋吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是诅咒啊！绝对是诅咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你说是啥子诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在神社的遗迹上建了这学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说那是神社的遗迹..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那里因为空袭已经被烧得什么都不剩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也不能改变那里曾经是神社的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有好好的驱邪消灾过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是没驱够啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没埋上人柱就在神社遗迹上建造学园而产生的诅咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该供奉的东西不供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自说自话的盖上了其他的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明老爷发怒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就算你们这么说 可现在也于事无补了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也只能趁现在把人柱补上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的下面还留着祀堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个洞马上就能进去祭拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样做能平息神明老爷的愤怒的话就好..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要埋的话埋谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这也没什么可以随便埋的死囚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算埋了罪人和马上要死的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明的愤怒也不会平息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁年轻的生命作为活祭品才是最适合的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..小孩子是村子的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人身御供的人选要是让村里人知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都死了这么多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再多不见一个人 也没有人会担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他当成是因瘟疫而死的话 应该就不会有人察觉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要选谁当人身御供呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出一个红人 把这个抉择交给他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作铜人读作红人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铜矿山之神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用抽签在村民里选出一个红人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而红人所指的那个孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要被当作人柱埋在神社的遗迹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异调查部的部室？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑到哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是墙壁上没有开孔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被听到了吗..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没听到的话就不会逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋办啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 祀堂好像就在这附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这个的时候吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别让他给溜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有这种事..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡饭多有见谅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样..那拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 夕子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也跟你们住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色 好很多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是普通的感冒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人说要把小孩子当做人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不忍心放任小浅一个人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把她叫来一起住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们好像都忙不过来了 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的空房间也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把热茶喝下去暖暖身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在体力正弱的时候要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的得瘟疫的话就不得了了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又全看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我可以一起进来洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可..不不不不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人会很不安吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 那些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都什么年代了还用人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不会被允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是地上汽车跑天上飞机飞的科学时代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种迷信能救得了谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须做点什么来阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 如果做那种事让姐姐卷入什么危险的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没想过只让自己得救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是姐姐你 只有这点不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请珍重自己一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这个正需要大家互相扶持的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能自己一个人逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 为什么不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子小姐 是在为夕子学姐而担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的月亮..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐原来..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么一位感情丰富的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个普通的女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经叫医生以后来这边帮你看病了 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 东西都乱丢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感冒又反复了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子 小浅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在客厅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅到什么时候还在客厅里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我去洗澡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就没看见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我马上就回房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要补一补吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 衣服破成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..置物小屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们得逞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小浅啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史已经证明了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们..在干什么啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小..浅？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人大人叫出了名字啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人大人叫出了名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人大人指出了活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人大人选出了活祭品..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人大人选定了人柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚骨折了..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分..太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这种事 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能治得好人的病啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会有人得救呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅不用当人柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我成为人柱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小浅和紫子就不会有事..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事..太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样..就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..祀堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以勉强自己动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊 好怕会死掉..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再动了 夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来..我好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚断了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫大夫来 来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我从这里放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都肯做 什么都会听你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听得见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么..我做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！为什么！为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么..好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷..好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子..好饿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么..我明明没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都..没有做错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁决定我是人柱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红人..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夕子学姐..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明待她这么温柔..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全因为那孩子叫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对..不是那孩子的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子..我好恨那孩子..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子..难不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕子学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那孩子的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..好难受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以..不可以恨小浅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的不是我..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是别的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会..含恨..而死...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 恨的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恨..好恨..好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨把我当成人柱妄图自己苟活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨杀死我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恨..好恨..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恨..好恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是影夕子的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是..夕子学姐的怪谈的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我离弃掉的你..我好恨
